text: John Chaloner Alabaster was born 11 July, 1930 and died 9 April, 2024 in Cromwell. He was a New Zealand cricketer who played 21 tests from 1955 to 1972 taking 49 wickets. He was the brother of Gren Alabaster. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 births Category:2024 deaths Category:New Zealand cricketers
